I found that changing the lambda from lines 556 to 561 fixed my issue:

    [out_z, z_pixels](int z_pixel_index, int other_pixel_index) {
        const unsigned short a = out_z[other_pixel_index];
        const unsigned short b = z_pixels[z_pixel_index];
        out_z[other_pixel_index] = a ? std::min(a,b) : b;
    })

Not sure why std::min couldn't generate correct implementation, but this seemed to resolve my problems.

